              .pc-column.pc-col3
                a.swipebox(rel='1', href='http://content.parkcameras.com/5/1/images/landing_pages/Canon_area1.jpg')
                  img(src='http://content.parkcameras.com/5/1/images/landing_pages/Canon_area1.jpg', alt='Park Cameras Canon')
                
              .pc-column.pc-col3
                a.swipebox(rel='1', href='http://content.parkcameras.com/5/1/images/landing_pages/Canon_area2.jpg')
                  img(src='http://content.parkcameras.com/5/1/images/landing_pages/Canon_area3.jpg', alt='Park Cameras Canon')
              
            .pc-wrapper.pc-column.pc-col1.pc-competition
              
              hr

              h3 About the Prize: 

              p Take to the skies in this 60 minute hot air balloon adventure, where you’ll be able to breathe in spectacular 360 degree panoramas and uninhibited views for miles in all directions, all the while experiencing a unique sense of freedom. Available seven days a week, with a choice of over 100 locations around the UK to choose from, this will be a great opportunity to grab your new Canon camera and get ready for some sensational photo opportunities.

              p.pc-spacer-l Once you’ve touched back down on terra firma, you’ll toast your landing in style together with a glass of Champagne each and a certificate signed by your pilot and endorsed by Sir Richard Branson. You’ll then be collected from your landing spot and whisked back to base to conclude your memorable experience. To make the memories last even longer, you’ll also receive a gift hamper complete with sparkling wine and chocolates.

              a.pc-btn-standard(href='https://www.parkcameras.com/bc/4-2528/canon/digital-cameras', target='_blank', title='Canon Digital Cameras') Canon Digital Camera Range
              
